Jayde is none the wiser, scrambling up onto the table itself for a 
better view.  "I've heard that one come out of a lot of mouths.  This 
gizmo should have been scrap metal by now."  She lays out on her side 
invitingly with her head propped up on an elbow, knowing that this 
Maximal can't reach her.  Since she's facing Yggdrasil, she doesn't 
realize that Torin has crept into the room.  The lizard-bot puts a 
finger to his metallic lips, indicating for Yggdrasil to ingore him.  
This would appear to be the Rogue equivalent of a practical joke 
taking shape.
